{"tid":1162712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國人今後到英國旅行 可使用機場自動閘門通關","createTime":"2019-05-20T04:37:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T04:42:05.000Z","uid":139611,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1360919a5463d9cd62fbac6c33bbeb53be9761f9","tid":1162712,"uid":139611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T04:37:14.000Z","msg":"新加坡人今後到英國旅行時，可在15個機場使用更快捷的自動閘門通關。<br />\n<br />\n這個電子護照（ePassport）自動通關服務原先只開放非英國和歐盟公民，如今擴大開放給來自新加坡、澳大利亞、加拿大、冰島、日本、新西蘭、瑞士、韓國和美國等國家的旅客。<br />\n<br />\n乘坐「歐洲之星」（Eurostar）火車抵達英國時，國人也能使用這項服務通關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.zaobao.com.sg/realtime/singapore/story20190520-957984?amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zaobao.com.sg%2Frealtime%2Fsingapore%2Fstory20190520-957984%3Famp&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ1y3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=672c1b7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.zaobao.com.sg/realtime/singapore/story20190520-957984?amp</a>"},{"pid":"e5192cac41fee438aa792fd45a4a8fd2ba5ca822","tid":1162712,"uid":78791,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T04:38:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"132422e125f97bc7ed69224fe9e81e408a7dfea5","tid":1162712,"uid":144,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T04:38:41.000Z","msg":"BNO又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b6ad804cb4aca8ae4689a63593be438e0995e6","tid":1162712,"uid":139611,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T04:38:57.000Z","msg":"係新加坡人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n火車頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ae82a3c47eb7006d4afc8ba271e26707a3d47e","tid":1162712,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e5192cac41fee438aa792fd45a4a8fd2ba5ca822","tid":1162712,"uid":78791,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTim